  title: Bell Rings at 3:11 Tomorrow
  bodyText: 'Ding.


    No guests. No movement outside.

    Just rain against the
    neon vacancy sign.

    When you rewind the security camera footage, the recording
    skips forward by exactly seventeen seconds each time.'
